          <p>St. Catharines requires licensing for all STR operators:</p>

          <h3>Application Requirements</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Proof of principal residence</strong> (183+ days/year)</li>
            <li><strong>Electrical safety certificate</strong> from licensed contractor</li>
            <li><strong>$2,000,000 liability insurance</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Designated agent</strong> within 1-hour response time</li>
            <li><strong>Floor plan</strong> showing rental areas</li>
            <li><strong>Fire safety compliance</strong> documentation</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>License Terms</h3>
