          <h2 id="demerit-system">The Demerit Point System</h2>
          <p>St. Catharines uses a graduated enforcement system:</p>

          <blockquote class="bylaw-quote">
            "A licensee who accumulates five (5) demerit points shall have their licence suspended for three (3) months. Ten (10) points results in revocation. Fifteen (15) points results in revocation with no right of appeal."
            <cite>St. Catharines By-law 2023-060</cite>
          </blockquote>

