          <ul>
            <li><strong>Minor violations</strong> (documentation issues): 1-2 points</li>
            <li><strong>Moderate violations</strong> (noise, parking): 2-3 points</li>
            <li><strong>Serious violations</strong> (safety issues, overcrowding): 4-5 points</li>
          </ul>

          <p>The escalating consequences mean:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>2-3 moderate violations = suspension</strong></li>
            <li><strong>4-5 moderate violations = revocation</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Points don't reset</strong> - they accumulate over time</li>
          </ul>

