              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="callout-content">
              <strong>Plan ahead:</strong> Scheduling a licensed electrical contractor can take time. Start this process early in your application timeline. The certificate is required before your license can be issued.
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 id="insurance">Insurance Requirements</h2>
          <p>St. Catharines requires standard STR insurance coverage:</p>

          <blockquote class="bylaw-quote">
            "The licensee shall maintain liability insurance of no less than two million dollars ($2,000,000) covering the short-term rental operation."
            <cite>St. Catharines By-law 2023-060</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <p>Key requirements:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>$2,000,000 minimum</strong> liability per occurrence</li>
            <li><strong>Must specifically cover</strong> STR operations</li>
            <li><strong>Certificate required</strong> with application</li>
            <li><strong>Maintain continuously</strong> - gaps violate the license</li>
